            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "ill say the exact truths about this school\ngood sides:\n*Maximum of the old teachers who are still in this school are great. we can easily clear our doubts and the students get a clear conception about the subjects.even new teaches are also very friendly and they are also great.\n*To be honest the environment of the schools is best. like 0 chaos in the school,disciplined. Best environment for study.the students can focus easily on the subjects.\n*Still most of the students have a good behavior and are friendly\n* we have numerous facilities like smartboards , ac, aquaguards etc making the environment hygienic and comfortable to study.\n*Some fun activities(non physical) are held every week eg:- drawing,writing practice, crafts, spoken english,reading etc.\n*many festivals are held with great entertainment.\n\nBest school if u want your child to peruse a great future only through studies.\n\ndown sides\n*The sports is not encouraged in this school. Yes sports festival is held every year with a lot of enthusiasm. But thats the only day.\n*Sports teachers try to avoid playground activities, only indoor games are played but it is negligible. Where only yoga is more prioritized. Karate is also there but maximum days the teacher is absent and doesnt teach a thing . the students just sit and sir gossips with us.\n*0 sports no participation in competitions in physical games\n* the students get only one day as games period and nothing entertaining happens there.\n\nif u want to develop your child in physical fitness,sorry to say u cant get it here\n\nMy respected principal mam, if u improve these downsides then your dpss will be the best school in all over barasat.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
